## ⚠️ Common Mistakes

| Mistake | Better Approach |
|---------|-----------------|
| No split validation | Validate sum = total amount |
| Balance as single value | Track per user-pair |
| No notification on events | Use Observer pattern |
| Tight coupling | Use Strategy for split types |

